text: Václav Neumann (29 October 1920 – 2 September 1995) is an Czech conductor, violinist, violist, and opera director. ==Discography== ;Studio albums * Dvorák: Symphonies Nos. 1-3 (2003) * Mahler: Symphonie Nr. 5 (2006) ==References== Category:1920 births Category:1995 deaths Category:Musicians from Prague
